This repository does NOT contain personal data, real wealth records, real ownership chains,
or trained model artefacts derived from real administrative microdata. All data included
in the repository are deterministically generated synthetic fixtures that mimic the schema
of Swedish administrative registers without reproducing any real individual's information.

Processing of Swedish administrative microdata for research purposes is conducted exclusively
inside the secure environment provided by Statistiska Centralbyran (SCB) under the terms of
Lag (2001:99) om den officiella statistiken and Offentlighets- och sekretesslagen (2009:400),
chapter 24. No such data are present in this repository.
